	abstract = {Knutson JS, Harley MY, Hisel TZ, Chae J. Improving hand function in stroke survivors: a pilot study of contralaterally controlled functional electric stimulation in chronic hemiplegia.
Objective
To assess the feasibility of a new stroke rehabilitation therapy for the hemiparetic hand.
